		"description": "<p>This small necklace bears a flame idol&mdash;like the birthmark that Milton Fremont had upon his hand&mdash;made of silver hanging from a silver chain.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><em><strong>Banish the Dark.</strong></em> While you are within 500 miles of the island of Flame&rsquo;s Rest and have an unobstructed line of effect to the Silver Flame, you can use a bonus action to grasp the necklace and point it at an area of darkness you can see that is up to 20 feet in radius. The area of darkness becomes brightly lit for the next minute and the darkness is dispelled.</p>\n<p>Alternatively, you can use this property while not able to access the Silver Flame. Once you have used this property in that way, you cannot do so again until the next dawn.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Silver Essence.</strong></em> While wearing this necklace, your melee and ranged weapon attacks are considered to be both magical and silvered.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Silver Light.</strong></em> This trinket shines with silver light in a 15-foot radius and dim silver light for an additional 15 feet. You can use an action to increase or decrease the light and dim light radiuses by 5 feet, up to a maximum of 30 feet each or down to a minimum of 10 feet each.</p>",
